{"tid":910673,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]到底譚仔炸醬應該點食","createTime":"2018-11-21T10:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T07:23:20.000Z","uid":9938,"like":264,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":124,"replies":[{"pid":"b34abd0e271ea5cf522759f02c93add55311eea1","tid":910673,"uid":9938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:50:26.000Z","msg":"岩先坐一枱人三個互不相識<br />\n三個都有點到炸醬<br />\n<br />\n我就用匙羹筆半羹炸醬再夾啲米線一齊食<br />\n<br />\n另一位女士就好似食沾麵咁得閒夾幾條米線落碗炸醬度撈兩撈<br />\n<br />\n仲有嗰位男士就一下子將成碗炸醬倒落碗米到<br />\n<br />\n到底應該點樣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n圖：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/21/185005_ac4b3e6c2710018ad4e0da3e83ae35ea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F21%2F185005_ac4b3e6c2710018ad4e0da3e83ae35ea.png&h=00961ba0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc337d473c48935f83b2cb817ba5e75144afc6c2","tid":910673,"uid":4525,"like":1458,"dislike":17,"score":1441,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:52:42.000Z","msg":"倒落張枱奶"},{"pid":"be9d9ad43f1bbdfed6a5e95fc645e1ee221d9b41","tid":910673,"uid":98232,"like":27,"dislike":4,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:53:30.000Z","msg":"我係2食法 撈面咁撈"},{"pid":"b5585a39679c7e77da095844e8054426011470de","tid":910673,"uid":77473,"like":139,"dislike":4,"score":135,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7465bc41011715c1d2443742125c68c5cc38ed9e","tid":910673,"uid":18913,"like":76,"dislike":4,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:56:42.000Z","msg":"就咁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"