7b","tid":910673,"uid":47966,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:12:25.000Z","msg":"第四種食法係分開就咁食"},{"pid":"7679321b82aea43d49952bf722a8da3aa59c6bef","tid":910673,"uid":280,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:12:45.000Z","msg":"有冇食過沾麵呀⋯⋯同一道理 <br />\n夾起米線 係pat屎到順時針搞兩野"},{"pid":"877113d6558f3ae17295634000cc21ea675ba826","tid":910673,"uid":71508,"like":168,"dislike":16,"score":152,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:13:18.000Z","msg":"你啱<br />\n女人啱<br />\n第3個係on9仔<br />\n不過依啲人地中意點食就點食<br />\n冇乜可以比較同恥笑"},{"pid":"1fe16c5ef7e7d6a4b5ffdaf76257800ce05ee930","tid":910673,"uid":153679,"like":33,"dislike":74,"score":-41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:17:28.000Z","msg":"將d湯倒落碗炸醬<br />\n我既習慣係三小匙既份量<br />\n太多會沖淡炸醬既肉味<br />\n太少又會太杰<br />\n以前長輩會教<br />\n食麵前飲一啖肉湯 唔好吞 吐返出黎 令口腔充滿炸醬既肉香同湯底既清爽 之後食一啖麵 <br />\n食到中段 口腔開始畀其他配菜味道蓋過 呢個時候 可以夾一小攝米線落炸醬到 令每條米線都充滿炸醬味<br />\n食到最後 可以將餘下既炸醬倒落碗入面 一口將清湯 炸細醬同米線吞入肚 好味!"},{"pid":"db168202f782bee8321ed62b3366e565a54b9be9","tid":910673,"uid":71768,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"好似啲卡通片咁<br />\n<br />\n昂高個頭 將碗麵同炸醬倒落個口到吞晒落肚"},{"pid":"4d1ce5130e5779549277b72f1d39db54c033b73d","tid":910673,"uid":194560,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:15:54.000Z","msg":"倒落張枱整條直線之後用鼻索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267c1d859b08e56e4ca9237a53a0d7721bb9977c","tid":910673,"uid":217092,"like":144,"dislike":2,"score":142,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"叫完之後唔撚食<br />\n將譚仔張單沾滿炸醬 然後遞比個收銀"},{"pid":"9fd1e6907ebf53bfd99a5127214ed0879232696f","tid":910673,"uid":49197,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:53:25.000Z","msg":"我係你果種食法"},{"pid":"b1c736845452f67b3aa4a0386facc38d9d6d803c","tid":910673,"uid":46435,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:55:59.000Z","msg":"叫多個蒜泥白肉 將白肉啲鼓油同蒜泥撈埋落啲炸醬 之後一半醬拎黎食白肉 一半醬拎黎夾上啲米線到食"},{"pid":"0838a99f34c6bb2238a25cb315d8af39735d66fc","tid":910673,"uid":8219,"like":51,"dislike":3,"score":48,"quote":{"pid":"1fe16c5ef7e7d6a4b5ffdaf76257800ce05ee930","tid":910673,"uid":153679,"like":33,"dislike":74,"score":-41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:17:28.000Z","msg":"將d湯倒落碗炸醬<br />\n我既習慣係三小匙既份量<br />\n太多會沖淡炸醬既肉味<br />\n太少又會太杰<br />\n以前長輩會教<br />\n食麵前飲一啖肉湯 唔好吞 吐返出黎 令口腔充滿炸醬既肉香同湯底既清爽 之後食一啖麵 <br />\n食到中段 口腔開始畀其他配菜味道蓋過 呢個時候 可以夾一小攝米線落炸醬到 令每條米線都充滿炸醬味<br />\n食到最後 可以將餘下既炸醬倒落碗入面 一口將清湯 炸細醬同米線吞入肚 好味!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:57:21.000Z","msg":"以為新潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647c91b45e4281668a33b8de1323c1d5d7f07f1c","tid":910673,"uid":15483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:58:50.000Z","msg":"我係用你果種做法，白肉都係咁食<br />\n<br />\n不過之後冇手玩電話又食勁耐就放棄左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6fb54af8fb834cf8399b6ec89e20ff0620f125","tid":910673,"uid":85132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T15:00:53.000Z","msg":"乜原來要後撈麵架， 我下次試下撈酸菜食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a9990423a9cef2f747a070c0216c9d270f1c04","tid":910673,"uid":57505,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T15:03:49.000Z","msg":"倒咗啲湯<br />\n將肉醬直接撐而麵"},{"pid":"bcdae96b5266582c00560dfc02eddaac5b361469","tid":910673,"uid":19646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T15:08:54.000Z","msg":"緊係夾麵包啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62377ba22dd1c90fe059d05e1f55f99ca7af9512","tid":910673,"uid":172823,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T15:11:58.000Z","msg":"似pat屎所以從來唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb64adb556474f1b1224d5efa34d3e981f27d0a","tid":910673,"uid":134864,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTim