e":{"pid":"2c6edfb6793f1e834b4e0c20a79f0e04b746cc16","tid":910673,"uid":63877,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e18e58bcb5e743fb8cca1732edc556191a6e2c25","tid":910673,"uid":49263,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T17:08:25.000Z","msg":"所以話你哋唔識嘢<br />\n其實仲有一種食法<br />\n首先拎去起碗炸醬 舉高望住個阿姐 打個眼色<br />\n好似咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個時候個阿姐應該就會知你用意<br />\n佢會唔出聲走返入去<br />\n呢個係一個暗示<br />\n然後你就起身跟佢入去<br />\n跟住佢入到一間房<br />\n佢就會拎一大桶炸醬出嚟<br />\n然後佢就會剝晒衫瞓喺張枱到<br />\n咁你就可以成桶炸醬由頭淋落佢到直到全身<br />\n你就可以開始由頭舐到落腳趾<br />\n最後就舐佢炸醬西<br />\n呢個就係譚仔姐體盛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T17:41:05.000Z","msg":"好尷尬 心諗做乜9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T17:47:12.000Z","msg":".........."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T01:01:14.000Z","msg":"幽默感哩家嘢........"},{"pid":"1900a20953fdfb984f00d867ac13c5a5e0d7c493","tid":910673,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T01:06:32.000Z","msg":"炸醬呢個問題可以整個心理測驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw我同樓主一樣食法"},{"pid":"d4746814e5cd3dfbf9c2fcb6ef6518f3856fccdb","tid":910673,"uid":47954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T01:09:05.000Z","msg":"最正宗的食法：將炸醬同米線倒落亞姐個口，浪幾下，再吐出來先食。"},{"pid":"b8f511abc0384c012e42fac74b83c1839b32a51b","tid":910673,"uid":164980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T01:10:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72d5b58b532b7d6290d235588c2b60ec0557c895","tid":910673,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T01:57:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcb519d2a67b84d34d7eccc1f3d97911ab633062","tid":910673,"uid":214519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T02:12:46.000Z","msg":"放喺粒lin 再奶"},{"pid":"8d4a4857c1a6e58b9d40d36f67e712c60cc84f58","tid":910673,"uid":29297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T02:13:36.000Z","msg":"畀狗食"},{"pid":"b0bc67f032a43ece5f248afd44d44f51cf12acaa","tid":910673,"uid":150716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T02:33:31.000Z","msg":"唔係講笑<br />\n炸醬麵，起源於山東,而鼻祖起源於漢代<br />\n當時有所謂三羹而不沾碗既始祖食法<br />\n一羹麵放於口左方, <br />\n一羹炸醬放於口右方, <br />\n最後一羹湯放於口中<br />\n再以舌頭把三者溶合, <br />\n清湯把炸醬之濃中和麵之淡,口部產生不能形容之美味<br />\n 其時千萬不要立即吞下, 應口含半小時為佳, 因為要待口水既產生與炸醬麵產生不可解釋既奇妙化學作用!!<br />\n故食炸醬麵之古人 多為在閒聊無所是事或不是生產既貴族 專利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9685b5ae035598ce452b3c475535930990c914f","tid":910673,"uid":98551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T02:36:26.000Z","msg":"成碗飲"},{"pid":"579dfbeb771941f42368696925bccdb302f9d687","tid":910673,"uid":53530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T02:45:39.000Z","msg":"食完個米線 之後淨食肉醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c95acac5d8f2ecb5a76311d696503bcbd6ed204f","tid":910673,"uid":43117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:01:59.000Z","msg":"你鐘意食嘔吐物？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b774d017cdee9991493f77eb47443f5a8f6c982","tid":910673,"uid":151311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:57:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fc339aed4bf9fc265393860572250336672c2e1","tid":910673,"uid":55755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T18:11:11.000Z","msg":"皮下注射<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782543f609022571089563cce3f3fd22dde549ae","tid":910673,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:59:39.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣<br />\n當咗係中式肉醬意粉"},{"pid":"cb43fb704fb89594c35652fcaa48f462ecd7dfc9","tid":910673,"uid":9938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T06:21:52.000Z","msg":"屌 岩先又食譚仔聽到隔離枱落單<br />\n「要炸醬 